Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎住在这里的人走得很匆忙\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Whoever left here left in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,‎来点光吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A little light?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎说到走得匆忙\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Speaking of leaving in a hurry,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你真的想躲开扎姆菲尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}you really wanted to get away from Zamfir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.64,0:00:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎坐下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎床很舒服\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Comfy bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这就是你想我们独处的原因吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Is this why you wanted us to be alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想躲开所有人至少那么一小会\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I wanted to get away from everyone else for five fucking minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们几周来疲于应对\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All we've been doing for weeks is reacting,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一件事接着另一件事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}being bounced from one thing to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有时间思考和讨论 ‎才会做到最好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And we do best when we've got time to think and talk things over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.59,0:01:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我很高兴你这么想\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm glad you think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.05,0:01:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我又不是很傻\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm not completely stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我很高兴你这么想\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm glad you think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.93,0:01:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎哈哈 真好笑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Ha ha. Very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎听着 我们不再被动应对 ‎开始主动出击\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Listen, we need to stop reacting and start acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就算被杀 我宁愿选择出击\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If I'm gonna get killed, I'd rather choose it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也不愿意落入别人的圈套\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}than get tricked into it by someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你想从哪里说起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Where would you like to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎从头说起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}At the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们还没有陷入困境的时候\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}before we find ourselves backed into the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是你们给我送的信吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You sent me a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎欢迎来到德内什蒂\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Welcome to Danesti.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想这里从前有过好日子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I presume it's seen better days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎更平静的日子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Quieter ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是村长格丽塔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm Greta, the village headwoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎叫我阿鲁卡多吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Call me Alucard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不用特指\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No "The."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎马里乌斯…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Did Marius...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的是你的骑手吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Was that your rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎很遗憾\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他在路上遇袭受伤 失血过多而亡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He was attacked en route and bled out from his wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他的马驮着他走完剩下的路 ‎手里还拿着你的信\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}His horse carried him the rest of the way with your message in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎哦\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我很遗憾\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们不仅失去了他\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, he's not the only one we've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但他是他家最后一个人 ‎所以才冒险上路\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But he was the last of his family, which is why he risked the journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我还是希望…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Still, I'd hoped...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想这就是希望得到的结果\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's what hoping gets you, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我还要救很多人 阿鲁卡多\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have a lot more people to save, Alucard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎趁着还能休息 大家休息一下吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Get some rest, everybody, while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你们遭到攻击多久了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}How long have you been under attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎四天了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎开始只有一个畜生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}First it was just one of those bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,每晚越来越多\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}More every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们昨晚勉强撑下来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We barely made it through last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,‎很幸运 只死了三分之一的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We're lucky only a third of us are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你愿意帮我们吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Will you help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我肯定能帮你做些什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm sure I can do something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我对用魔法打仗不感兴趣\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm not interested in magic tricks and one fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎照顾这些人是我的责任\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}These people are under my care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎无论花多长时间 ‎你愿意留下来保护他们吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Will you stay and defend them for as long as it takes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎-我说过…  ‎-请你理解\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- I said... - You have to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不了解你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你在三十多公里外住了几个月\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You've been 20-odd miles away for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你在森林里跑来跑去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You creep around the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你把尸体挂在奇怪城堡外面的木桩上\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You've got bodies on stakes outside your weird castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你明显是半吸血鬼 你身上有酒味\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're obviously half-vampire, and you stink of wine,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎在我看来 你差不多是个疯子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and you appear to me to be at least half-crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我能想到的救兵只有你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But you were the only possible advantage I could think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不想对低调的霸气表示钦佩\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't need to be impressed by low-key swagger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想让你答应救这些人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I need you to commit to saving these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎因为我要是救不了他们 ‎我的生命也不值得留恋\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because my life isn't worth living if I can't save theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎说完了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All done?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,‎可以吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那我说完了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Then I'm all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,‎谢谢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎刚才的出场真的很精彩\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And that was one hell of an entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没错 确实如此\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes, indeed so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你真是个非常英勇的年轻人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You really are a very impressive young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不擅长令人作呕的暴力 请你理解\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sickening violence isn't especially in my skill set, you understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我能认出行家 无论是哪个领域\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but I can recognize a fellow expert, no matter what the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎天啊 这家伙\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, God. This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你是阿德里安·特佩斯吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You would be Adrian Tepes, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎请允许我介绍一下自己\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do allow me to present myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是圣日耳曼伯爵\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am the Count Saint Germain,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎常驻欧洲各大宫廷的学者\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}scholar in residence to many of the great courts of Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你为什么躲在瓦拉吉亚的厕所里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why are you cowering in a latrine hut in Wallachia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是厕所吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh.  Is this a latrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我还以为有人给吓坏了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I just... I just thought someone had gotten very scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我在旅行 先生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm traveling, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎瓦拉吉亚的动荡时代\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Interesting times in Wallachia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我觉得一位学者应该亲眼见证\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I felt that a man of letters should bear witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,‎目前为止你的旅行开心吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And are you enjoying your tourism so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这段旅程...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}it has been, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎给人很多启发\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}enlightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎圣日耳曼 陛下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Saint Germain, Your Majesty,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎欧洲各大宫廷的神秘学家 书记员和法律顾问\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}occultist, scribe, and counsel to the great courts of Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,‎圣日耳曼 皇帝陛下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Saint Germain, Your Imperial Majesty,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎占星家 情报员和学者\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}astrologist, intelligencer, and... and scholar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎圣日耳曼 殿下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Saint Germain, Your Royal Highness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎占卜师 预言家和黑魔法巫师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}soothsayer, prophet, and practitioner of the dark arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎圣日耳曼 阁下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Saint Germain, Your Grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎图书馆员 书记员和学者\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}librarian, scribe, and scholar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎圣日耳曼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Saint Germain,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎您卑微的仆人...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}your humble servant in, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎听候您的差遣\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}whatever you may need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎别对这样的人动手动脚 ‎你这粗鲁的小混蛋\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do not grope for a person like that, you rude little clump of frog shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎圣日耳曼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Uh, Saint Germain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎利索的武力不是我的强项 ‎不过 我肯定认得出行家 深表钦佩\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Swift violence is not my forte, but I certainly recognize and admire an expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你游历过这么多地方 令人难以置信\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The sheer breadth of your travels is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你回到这个破地方 ‎老实说 让我感到惊讶\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm frankly amazed you ever bothered coming back to this shit hole,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也很高兴\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我需要钱 但我也想在图书馆里寻宝\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I needed the money, but I also wanted to pick through the library here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我知道世上有一本书\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I understood there was a volume
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎讲述一个叫无限回廊的地方\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}regarding a place called the Infinite Corridor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我找不到这本该死的书\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but I can't find the damned thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就是这个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就是这本书\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没错 让我们踏上一生难忘的旅程\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And, yes, offering us the journey of a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎如果你真的想这么做...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If you really want to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那我们就去做\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}then that is what we will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎为你做什么都行\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎抓住我的手\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Take my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎求你了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎无限回廊是通往许多其它世界的通道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The Infinite Corridor is a route to many other worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎事实上 这是个传送门系统\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It is in fact a system of doors to other lands,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎通往跟我们时间和空间不同的世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}separated from our own by space and time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:10:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎很久以前 ‎我在无限回廊中...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A long time ago, I lost someone very dear to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎失去了挚爱之人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}in the Infinite Corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎从那以后 ‎我一直在寻找再次进入的方法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I have been looking for a way back in ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎通往回廊的入口很少 间隔很远\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Portals to the Corridor are few and far between,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎而且忽隐忽现\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and they drift in and out of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我要关闭回廊了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm closing the Corridor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎快出去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Get out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎谢谢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎谢谢你们两位\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Thank you both!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,‎后会有期\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'll see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎究竟在哪里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我知道就在这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I know it's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我只是… ‎我控制不了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I just... I have no control!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎为什么我控制不了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why can't I control this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我回来了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I made it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,‎喊一声 我就能找到你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Shout so I can find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你好啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hello, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你的朋友最近去了‎回廊里的另一个地方\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Your friend has recently moved on to another sphere within the Corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎很遗憾\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她去哪里了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But wh-where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这还真不好说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I cannot be certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我没有去找她...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have not looked for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎圣日耳曼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Saint Germain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你知道我吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我知道很多事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I know much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是炼金师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm an alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我也是炼金师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你不算\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你很久以前就半途而废了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You fell by the wayside long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我一直...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, I've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很忙 ‎但我仍然相信炼金术的目标\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}busy, but I still believe in the goals of the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎相信\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Believe in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎却不尽力吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not committed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,‎生活往往让人无法尽心尽力 对吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, life tends to mitigate against complete commitment, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她在哪里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Wh-where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以你发现自己来到这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And so you find yourself here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没有力量 不能控制...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}With no power, no control...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也没有前进的路\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and no way forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎根本不可能控制回廊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's impossible to control the Corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她在哪里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不 才不是呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你知道不是这样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You know it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你见过回廊被控制\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You've witnessed it being controlled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没错 是怪物控制的 他杀了几十个人 ‎用他们的灵魂做燃料\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yeah, by a monster who had dozens of people killed to use their souls as fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以别说控制不了回廊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So don't say it's impossible to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不是杀人狂\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am not a mass murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她在哪里 听到没\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Where is she, damn it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎圣日耳曼...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Saint Germain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎炼金术的真正目的是什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}what is the true goal of alchemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你记得吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还是说 你已经完全放弃了这条路\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Or have you left the path entirely?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这项壮举是伟大的工作 ‎协调世界的混乱\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The magnum opus, the great work, reconciling the chaos of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这项伟大工作的成果是什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And what is the result of the great work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎同体者 经过腐败和净化\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The Rebus, the putrefied and purified fusion
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎精神与物质融入男女同体的身体\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}of matter and spirit in a body both male and female.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是测试吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Is this a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎两个身体融为一体 圣日耳曼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Two bodies into one, Saint Germain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎两个灵魂\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Two souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你在开玩笑吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're not serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我看起来像开玩笑吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do I not look serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你是说炼金过程的最终成果\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're claiming that the final victory of the alchemical process
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是用同体者来控制无限回廊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}is using a Rebus to control the Infinite Corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那让我看看你的同体者\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Show me your damned Rebus, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不用管我的同体者\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}My Rebus cannot be looked upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是秩序和混乱的产物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It is a creature of order and chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎包含自然的人性和超自然的恐怖\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}of natural humanity and supernatural horror,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎经过火焰的净化 在地狱里腐烂\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}purified by fire and sent to rot in Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你听懂我在说什么吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我希望没听懂\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I hope not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:14:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你懂的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你懂你的炼金术必须召唤什么东西吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You understand what your alchemy must summon, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你说的是必须召唤"谁"吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You mean "who," don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我必须召唤 结合 融为一体的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Who I must summon, bind, and fuse into one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎只有这样你才能有力量穿越回廊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Only then will you be able to travel the Corridor with power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我要给你看这个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I will show you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这掌管着许多人的死亡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is charged with many deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎它会在你选择的任何地方打开回廊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It will open the Corridor wherever you choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎如果我拿走这个 ‎你就会被困在回廊里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If I take this, then I leave you stranded in the Corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我完全控制了穿越回廊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I travel the Corridor with complete control.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我像女神一样 ‎每年穿过100个不同的宇宙\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I dance through a hundred different universes every year like a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我为什么要离开\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why would I ever want to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎谢谢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不用谢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You are welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这对你没用 ‎除非你尽力投入炼金术的工作\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is useless to you unless you commit to the work of alchemy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎完成你该做的事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and do what needs to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你不能帮我找到她吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Couldn't you just help me find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我已经尽力帮你了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've helped you as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎剩下的是你的使命 ‎不是我的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What remains is your task, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎要尽力\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Commit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我会的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我尽力了 我来了这里 不是吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am committed. I'm here, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你要做出牺牲\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You must sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我牺牲了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是失去了某些东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You have lost something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那不一样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That is not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但感觉是一样的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Bloody feels like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你要做出牺牲 ‎自愿放弃\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You must sacrifice, give willingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎放弃什么 留下什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Give what? What's left?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,‎放弃一切\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎牺牲你的伦理道德\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sacrifice your ethics, your morals.
